            <img src="<%= image_path "modules/site/issues/illo/avatar-preciselyalyss.png" %>" alt="" width="20" height="20" class="width-fit height-auto d-none d-md-block mr-1" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
            <span class="color-fg-muted text-truncate"><strong class="text-semibold color-fg-default">preciselyalyss</strong> mentioned this <span class="d-none d-md-inline">issue 4 days ago</span></span>
